snippet.title: Age of Empires Mobile | Cast | Dev Tean Diary for New Year New Age Livestream
snippet.description:
Governors, before you join the world of Age of Empires Mobile, our dev team wants to share their journey crafting this game! 

In this video, you can learn more about core gameplay and quickly start your journey when the game is released! 

- Producer Robin explains the development process of the game and the expectations behind it 
- Lead Game Designer Cross gives a brief intro of the dev team and how TiMi and World's Edge maximized their strengths during the development of Age of Empires Mobile 
- Senior Operation Manager Shay and Senior Game Designer Peter give a detailed overview of unique gameplay and strategic elements
